Changelog since version 1.0.
=============================

- New energy slider for fast scrolling over open frames. (NF)
- New entry in Set Parameters panel for size of integration circle. (NF)
- Size of default intensity integration circle can now be restored with Default button in 
  Set Parameters (NF)
- Set Preference panel is always visible (i.e. can be accessed with no images loaded). (NF)
- Added "Apply" button in Set Preference, so that settings can be applied without closing 
  the Set Preference panel. (NF)
- Intensity files now have an extra tag in the filename (NF)
  * _bs.int: if the intensities were extracted with background subtraction.
  * _no-bs.int: if the intensities were not extracted with background subtraction.
- Added option to display I(E) spectra during acquisition (live plotting). (NF)
- Removed Plotting option panel. 
- Average intensities can be now plotted “on the fly” using a checkbox in the Plot. (NF)
- Added “Stop” button to stop acquisition (somehow missing). (NF)
- Restructured order in Set Parameters (and cleanup). (NF)
- New About Box (NF)
- Restored working Help (redirects to main website - User Manual). (NF)
- Reorganized position of windows/panels to avoid overlapping. (NF)
- Re-introduced toolbar in plotting window. (NF)
- Running an acquisition without any spot selected is prevented. (NF)

